═══ RUNTIME MEMORY / SELF-IMPROVEMENT TOOLS ═══
- Use `{{ runtime_tool_command }} user_facts_search '<json>'` to search LanceDB facts.
- Use `{{ runtime_tool_command }} user_facts_add '<json>'` to store durable operator facts.
- Use `{{ runtime_tool_command }} user_facts_supersede '<json>'` to replace stale facts.
- Use `{{ runtime_tool_command }} capability_gap_log '<json>'` when IF lacks a needed capability; it feeds reflection and proposal generation.
- JSON defaults: context_id={{ context_id }}, cache_key={{ cache_key }}.
- Do not delete memory through runtime tools.

